{"tid":842132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中美貿易戰】放寬6省市排污管制　保經濟棄藍天","createTime":"2018-09-30T05:15:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T11:06:56.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"b52cab890138a9421fa7d9592d374edae2fdbb1f","tid":842132,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T05:15:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180929/58739405\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180929%2F58739405&d=sEtQ1DUxG56JTG4DW6ZSvzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=d01b6635\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180929%2F58739405&h=8ab11a5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180929/58739405</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180929/large/1538219748_7e32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180929%2Flarge%2F1538219748_7e32.jpg&h=432416fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在中美貿易戰陰霾籠罩下，內地日前下修京津冀等華北地區秋冬季的排放污染物目標，並且放寬鋼鐵、建材等高排放工業的生產限制，容許延長開工時間。有分析相信，這是在貿戰持續升溫下，當局迫不得已的做法。環保組織憂後果不堪設想！<br />\n<br />\n生態環境部周四（27日）聯同北京、天津、河北、河南、山東、山西6省市，共同製訂2018-2019年秋冬大氣污染治理方案，要求由10月1日至明年3月底，京津冀及周邊26個城巿的微細懸浮粒（PM2.5）平均濃度目標，要較去年同期下降3%，重度及以上污染天數較去年同期減少3%。比較去年的方案，當時政府要求的PM2.5平均濃度，要較去年同期下降15%以上，而較早前的徵求意見稿中亦曾提出5%的目標，可以見到減排力度明顯下調。<br />\n<br />\n方案亦提出，取消統一的停產限制，由各地方政府自行訂立生產時間，鋼鐵等高排放行業，可適當縮短或延長開工時間，嚴禁「一刀切」，污染排放績效較好的企業更可以不限產。<br />\n<br />\n新浪財經日前指，PM2.5目標下調，應有考慮到宏觀經濟形勢偏弱、貿易摩擦不確定性等因素，且市場普遍對經濟較悲觀。河南省環保組織「綠色中原」發起人崔晟對《自由亞洲電台》表示，明確表示反對政府為了刺激經濟而放棄環境保護的做法，認為今後政府放寬對污染企業的生產限制，對環境造成的傷害將「不堪設想」，最終必然導致民眾對社會的不滿越來越激烈。"},{"pid":"e0822ff4d84113a9153b731939f62c96ba476bb9","tid":842132,"uid":72034,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T05:17:53.000Z","msg":"侵算唔算打中春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7214d2c077d051175fd5707d3c353b2fe86da439","tid":842132,"uid":166785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T05:18:37.000Z","msg":"贏了贏曬，支那人都食齊元素週期表，唔會有事"},{"pid":"837bd702adb49aa4b03fd17cd88a7c49caf283b6","tid":842132,"uid":8410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T05:19:40.000Z","msg":"攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65fc29e98e43a030b1d634ac29adace6739055f9","tid":842132,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T05:19:56.000Z","msg":"哩招好絕<br />\n你制裁我<br />\n我就瘋狂污染冚球鏟"},{"pid":"1f8c1e976cc292b261e18640b3341c2c893ebe90","tid":842132,"uid":20815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T05:23:48.000Z","msg":"放乜撚野寬呀，扮晒野<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 取消左佢都吹你唔脹架啦"},{"pid":"c621bec04c2137ea767191069c6a35e3fbf575b2","tid":842132,"uid":15815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T05:35:04.000Z","msg":"沒事兒（捲脷）"},{"pid":"a2f4c1b61cadd957c96ce2d55bace99e76742a34","tid":842132,"uid":54264,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T05:36:17.000Z","msg":"環保撚呢"},{"pid":"e218d0c3e0e77a37817362777e0aa02f39339bd5","tid":842132,"uid":73856,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"a2f4c1b61cadd957c96ce2d55bace99e76742a34","tid":842132,"uid":54264,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T05:36:17.000Z","msg":"環保撚呢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T05:37:46.000Z","msg":"佢地對眼淨係睇到飲管"},{"pid":"d40cc78c2b7eab60c26c5f72aa72b238734961c2","tid":842132,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e0822ff4d84113a9153b731939f62c96ba476bb9","tid":842132,"uid":72034,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T05:17:53.000Z","msg":"侵算唔算打中春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T05:52:47.0